### 닉네임 중복 확인
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/validate-nickname?nickname={{nickname}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 사용자 닉네임 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/{{memberId}}/nickname
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 사용자의 모든 채팅방 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/{{memberId}}/chatrooms
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json
